subSubSection.paragraph:
Included species (alphabetically).
Microphorites deploegi Nel, Perrichot, Daugeron & Néraudeau, 2004: 24
(Charentese amber, uppermost Albian, Lower Cretaceous, France );
M . erikai Bramuzzo & Nel, 2017: 590
(lowermost Eocene, Oise amber, France );
M . extinctus Hennig, 1971: 16
(Lebanese amber, Lower Cretaceous, Barremian, Jezzine, Lebanon );
